data.description: Fully renovated in 2018 condo in very desirable waterfront community on a private road. Includes 24 hour security patrol, gated entrance, intercom, full property maintenance, snow removals, and trash collection. Large one bedroom with updated kitchen including stainless steel appliances and granite countertops. Gas & water is also included in dues. Laundry toom includes washer and dryer. New lighting and plumbing fixtures. Building includes newer elevators, common basement and many cosmetic upgrades. 1 car parking space in garage structure. Beautiful grounds includes in ground multiple pools, clubhouse, gazebo, fenced areas plus beautiful stunning views of Detroit River and downtown Detroit. Has direct access to the new Detroit Riverwalk. Also includes on site marina with boat facilities at additional cost.  Association fee included in land contract payment.
